PRIVACY NOTICE FOR USERS:

This software is designed to run entirely on your local machine and does not
transmit any data to external servers. However, you are responsible for:

1. Configuring privacy settings appropriately for your use case
2. Ensuring sensitive data is not accidentally committed to version control
3. Understanding that all data processing happens locally on your device

The maintainers of this software are not responsible for any data exposure
resulting from misconfiguration or improper use of this software.

